## 16.1 The AequNet Concept

### Blockchain-Based Internet Alternative

**Revolutionary Network Architecture:**
```julia
struct AequNet
 vision = """
 AequNet: A parallel internet running on aequchain nodes
 
 Core Concept:
 ‚îú‚îÄ Every aequchain node is also a network node
 ‚îú‚îÄ Data routed through blockchain network
 ‚îú‚îÄ Encrypted, censorship-resistant
 ‚îú‚îÄ No central control
 ‚îú‚îÄ Self-healing, resilient
 ‚îú‚îÄ Integrated with EDS economy
 ‚îî‚îÄ Free access for all members
 
 Advantages over traditional internet:
 ‚îú‚îÄ Censorship resistance (no single point of control)
 ‚îú‚îÄ Privacy by design (encrypted, anonymous possible)
 ‚îú‚îÄ Resilience (distributed, redundant)
 ‚îú‚îÄ Integrated payments (native cryptocurrency)
 ‚îú‚îÄ Verified identity (optional, blockchain-based)
 ‚îú‚îÄ No gatekeepers (peer-to-peer)
 ‚îî‚îÄ Community governed
 """
 
 architecture = NetworkArchitecture(
 layers=[
 Layer(
 name="Physical Layer",
 components=[
 "Fiber optic cables",
